{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fractured Core is a story-driven JRPG set in cyberpunk world where a group of mercenaries undertake a series of missions and slowly realize the world is not as it seems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1238990/extras/explore_the_world.png?t=1732521678\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1238990/extras/world.gif?t=1732521678\" />Travel through the immersive and diverse landscapes, from futuristic cityscapes, bleak slums and captivating countryside. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1238990/extras/captivating_storyline.png?t=1732521678\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1238990/extras/npc.gif?t=1732521678\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Follow the story of a group of mercenaries as they encounter various characters with their own story and problem.\u00a0From a pedestrian on the street to the higher ups of a multinational corporation, you decide whether to help them or\u00a0ignore their needs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1238990/extras/tactical_combat.png?t=1732521678\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1238990/extras/battle.gif?t=1732521678\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout your journey you will find various foes each with their own strengths and weaknesses. Take up your guns and blades or exploit the elements to your advantage. Stun them to deal massive amount of damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1238990/extras/suit_up_and_gear_up.png?t=1732521678\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1238990/extras/mod.gif?t=1732521678\" />Customize your characters to better suit your style, each with different elemental and combat proficiency. Equip them with various weapons and mods obtainable from your journey and find the right one that suit your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1238990/extras/key_features.png?t=1732521678\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">15-25 hours of play time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Various equipment to be crafted and modded.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Extensive character customization to suit a variety of playstyles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Highly detailed pixel art graphics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meticulously composed original soundtracks.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1238990/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732521678","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1238990/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732521678","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1238990/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732521678","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1238990/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732521678","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"